### =========================================================================
### 5. KITCHEN OPERATIONS & RIDER DISPATCH (Protected - Requires Staff Token)
### =========================================================================

### @name ViewCentralKitchenDashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

###

### @name FetchAvailableRiders
GET {{baseUrl}}/riders/available
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

###

### @name AssignRiderToOrder
### INSTRUCTIONS: Replace the ID in the URL with a real Order _id from MongoDB 
### and the riderId in the body with a real Rider _id.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ORDER_ID/assign
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

{
  "riderId": "REPLACE_WITH_REAL_RIDER_ID"
}

###

### @name AdvanceOrderStatus (Kitchen Staff Workflow)
### INSTRUCTIONS: Replace the ID in the URL with a real Order _id from MongoDB.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ORDER_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

{
  "statusState": "Preparing"
}

---

### =========================================================================
### 6. RIDER SHIFT LOGISTICS (Protected - Requires Rider Token)
### =========================================================================

### @name ToggleRiderShiftToActive
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/riders/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{riderToken}}

{
  "scheduleStatus": "Active/Idle"
}

###

### @name FetchMyAssignedDeliveries
GET {{baseUrl}}/riders/my-deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{riderToken}}

###

### @name MarkOrderAsDelivered (Rider Workflow)
### INSTRUCTIONS: Replace the ID in the URL with a real Order _id from MongoDB.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ORDER_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{riderToken}}

{
  "statusState": "Delivered"
}